    "We investigate the impact of increasing the number of fine-tuning epochs on the robustness of SHIP.",
    "Following the setup in (Huang et al., 2023a), we set the default training and fine-tuning epochs to four and two, respectively.",
    "We then explore the trigger's resilience to additional rounds of benign fine-tuning.",
    "Take the Mistral model and the dataset described in Section 5.2 as an example, utilizing the trigger with three components and employing UDS, we observe the effects of extending fine-tuning.",
    "As shown in Table 5, SHIP maintains ASR above 90% and CACC above 95%, with FTR and ITR lower than 3%, even after eight rounds of finetuning, which is twice the Hijacking epochs."
